      Subclasses of Command in itmo.labs.zavar.commands 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  AddCommand
      Adds a new item to the collection.
      class  AddIfMaxCommand
      Adds a new element to the collection if its value exceeds the value of the largest element in this collection.
      class  AddIfMinCommand
      Adds a new element to the collection if its value is less than that of the smallest element in this collection.
      class  AverageOfTSCommand
      Outputs the average value of the transferredStudents field for all items in the collection.
      class  ClearCommand
      Clears the collection.
      class  CountGreaterThanTSCommand
      Outputs the number of elements whose transferredStudents field value is greater than the specified value.
      class  ExecuteScriptCommand
      Reads and executes the script from the specified file.
      class  ExitCommand
      Terminates the program (without saving it to a file).
      class  HelpCommand
      Displays help for available commands.
      class  HistoryCommand
      Ouputs history of commands.
      class  InfoCommand
      Outputs information about the collection to the standard output stream.
      class  RemoveAnyBySCCommand
      Removes one element from the collection whose studentsCount field value is equivalent to the specified one.
      class  RemoveByIDCommand
      Deletes an item from the collection by its id.
      class  SaveCommand
      Saves the collection to a file.
      class  ShowCommand
      Outputs all elements of the collection in a string representation to the standard output stream.
      class  ShuffleCommand
      Shuffles the elements of the collection in a random order.
      class  UpdateCommand
      Updates the value of a collection element whose id is equal to the specified one.
